ort**: gap-analysis.md\n    89ŌåÆ- **Log**: gap-analysis.log\n    90ŌåÆ\n    91ŌåÆ## Iteration 5 ŌĆö 2026-03-25 ŌĆö OK\n    92ŌåÆ\n    93ŌåÆ**Item**: [backend] DB client methods: `insertReferralEarning`, `getPendingBalance`, `getReferralEarnings`, `getReferralStats`\n    94ŌåÆ**Status**: Done\n    95ŌåÆ**Changes**:\n    96ŌåÆ- Added `ReferralEarning` interface (id, referrer_wallet, referee_wallet, round_id, game_type, wager_lamports, fee_lamports, referrer_earned_lamports, referrer_rate_bps, referee_rebate_lamports, referee_rebate_rate_bps, created_at)\n    97ŌåÆ- Added `ReferralStats` interface (referred_count, active_count, total_volume_lamports, total_earned_lamports, pending_lamports)\n    98ŌåÆ- Added `normalizeReferralEarning()` helper to convert BIGINT columns to JS numbers\n    99ŌåÆ- Added 4 method signatures to `Db` interface + implementations in `createDb()`:\n   100ŌåÆ  - `insertReferralEarning(params)`: INSERT with all earning fields, RETURNING *, normalized\n   101ŌåÆ  - `getPendingBalance(wallet)`: SUM(referrer_earned where referrer) + SUM(referee_rebate where referee) - SUM(completed/pending/processing claims). Returns lamport string\n   102ŌåÆ  - `getReferralEarnings(wallet, page, limit)`: paginated SELECT by referrer_wallet, newest first, with totalPages count\n   103ŌåÆ  - `getReferralStats(wallet)`: single query returning referred_count, active_count (7d), total_volume, total_earned, pending_lamports\n   104ŌåÆ**Verification**: `pnpm lint` passed (18/18). Backend typecheck has 1 pre-existing error (HealthDeps in endpoints.test.ts) ŌĆö no new errors introduced.\n   105ŌåÆ\n   106ŌåÆ## Iteration 5 ŌĆö 2026-03-25T11:43:58Z ŌĆö OK\n   107ŌåÆ- **Log**: iteration-005.log\n   108ŌåÆ\n   109ŌåÆ## Iteration 6 ŌĆö 2026-03-25 ŌĆö OK\n   110ŌåÆ\n   111ŌåÆ**Item**: [backend] DB client methods: `insertReferralClaim`, `getReferralClaim`, `updateClaimStatus`, `getReferrerRate(wallet)`\n   112ŌåÆ**Status**: Done\n   113ŌåÆ**Changes**:\n   114ŌåÆ- Added `ReferralC